comments: Jaquez Jr. (MIA) and Banchero (ORL) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Highsmith (MIA) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Robinson (MIA) briefly grasps and releases Banchero's (ORL) arm as they engage and disengage with one another.

Wagner (ORL) places an arm against Adebayo's (MIA) side and the marginal contact does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.  The foul should be assessed to Banchero (ORL), who initiates illegal contact across Adebayo's right arm.
Martin (MIA) brings his off-arm to Queen's (ORL) chest and marginal contact occurs as Martin releases away during the drive.
Banchero (ORL) reaches in and initiates contact to Adebayo's (MIA) right arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Banchero (ORL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and any contact with Adebayo's (MIA) hand on the ball is incidental.

Replay review of the out of bounds called on Black (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Black is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and MIA retains possession.
Highsmith (MIA) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends during the driving shot attempt.
Martin (MIA) and Wagner (ORL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Highsmith (MIA) places a forearm against Banchero's (ORL) side and incidental contact occurs as Banchero loses control of the ball on his own.
Houstan (ORL) extends his arms forward and initiates contact with Highsmith (MIA) that affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.
Wagner (ORL) establishes himself in Highsmith's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Highsmith (MIA) avoids making body contact with Banchero (ORL) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
